title: INDIAN HILLS SENIOR COMMUNITY!
posting_body: ['*****COLD WEATHER IS HEADED OUR WAY!!!', '*****', '***WARM UP WITH SPECIALS THAT WILL NOT LAST!', '*', '**', 'We are offering a $100 Security Deposit for those who qualify!!!!', 'This special will NOT last!!!', 'Our Senior Community is secluded behind iron gates on 37 beautifully-landscaped acres.', 'Our 1-bedroom suites start at just $645/ month.', 'This plan comes complete with a large living room, formal dining room, fully-equipped, galley-style kitchen, large bedroom with a walk-in closet, full bath, and both a linen and hall closet.', 'Our units are each equipped with stove ranges, refrigerators, and dishwashers.', 'Our recent renovations include: new kitchens, suite upgrades, new flooring, intercom entry, and a choice of patio or balcony on most suites.', 'Our residents here at Indian Hills Senior Community enjoy...', 'FREE HEAT!!!!', 'WATER!!!!', 'GAS!!!!', 'SEWER and much more !!!!', 'Get in here!!!', '***$0 Pet Deposit*** We are a pet-friendly community where cats and small dogs are welcome!', 'Ample free parking, and garage parking available for a small monthly fee.', 'Housing vouchers accepted!!!', 'Please call📞 us at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a tour TODAY!!!!', 'OR visit our website at <URL>', 'Amenities', '*Heated Indoor Pool*', '*Fitness Center*', '*Computer Room*', '*Movie Theater*', 'just to name a few....', 'For more details...', 'Contact Indian Hills Senior Community at', 'show contact info', '👉 ****JANUARY SPECIALS*****👈']
